com.mmm.cms.homehealth.proto

Interface ScoringResultsIF

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ScoringResults

    public interface ScoringResultsIF
    Holds the HIPPS, OASIS Treatment Authorization, Version and Flag information accumulated during the Grouper scoring process.
    Author:
    3M Health Information Systems for CMS Home Health

      • getValidationEdits

        CollectionValidationEditsIF getValidationEdits()
        gets the collection of validation edits that should be applied to a scored record in order for the record to score properly - non-HH PPS related edits, such as payor code, may not be part of this collection, but may be.
        Returns:
        null if validation was not applied to a scored record, and a non-collection if the validation was applied, however, the collection may be empty if there were no edits.
